<div
  style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 30px 20px; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111827;"
>

  <a href="https://aestheticpixelstudio.com" target="_blank">
    <div
      style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"
    >
      <img
        src="https://aestheticpixelstudio.com/logoDark.png"
        alt="Aesthetic Pixel Studio Logo"
        style="width: 48px; height: 48px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 5px; border-radius: 8px;"
      />
      <span
        style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: -0.5px; color: #111827;"
      >
        Aesthetic Pixel Studio LLC
      </span>
    </div>
  </a>

  <div style="padding: 32px 0;">
    <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #111827;">Welcome aboard,
      {{name}}! 🚀</h2>

    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">
      We are absolutely thrilled to have you join us at
      <strong>Aesthetic Pixel Studio LLC
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
      <a
        href="{{loginLink}}"
        style="background-color: #000000; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px;"
      >
        Access Your Dashboard
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">
      If you have any questions, need help getting started, or want to discuss a
      project, just reply directly to this email. We are always here to help.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>